EN: We saw a waterfall flowing from the creek on top of the mountain.

ZH: 在田野的尽头，有一条曲曲折折的小溪。
EN: At the end of the field, there is a winding little stream.

ZH: 每年春天，小溪的两岸都开满了鲜花。
EN: Every spring, the banks of the brook are full of blossoms.

